it.eng.spagobi.meta.model.business
Interface BusinessModelPackage

All Known Implementing Classes:
BusinessModelPackageImpl
public interface BusinessModelPackage

The Package for the model. It contains accessors for the meta objects to represent

  • each class,
  • each feature of each class,
  • each enum,
  • and each data type

See Also:
BusinessModelFactory
